<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Payment Successful - ElevateU</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@600&family=Nunito&family=Roboto&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
        color: #1a1a1a;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 40px 30px;
        border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding-bottom: 30px;
      }
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 26px;
        margin: 0;
        color: #98CE00;
        font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      }
      .content {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333333;
        font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
      }
      .content strong {
        color: #1a1a1a;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        background-color: #98CE00;
        color: #000000;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      }
      .button:hover {
        background-color: #0DD8FC;
        color: #ffffff;
      }
      a.support-link {
        color: #0DD8FC;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 40px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #888888;
        font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Payment Successful</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{email}},</p>

        <p>Thank you for your payment. We have successfully received your payment of <strong>{{amount}}</strong> for your ElevateU subscription/service.</p>

        <p><strong>Transaction ID:</strong> {{transaction_id}}<br />
           <strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</p>

        <p>You can view your invoice or manage your account anytime using the button below:</p>

        <div style="text-align:center;">
          <a href="{{account_url}}" target="_blank" class="button">
            View My Account
          </a>
        </div>

        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to <a href="{{support_url}}" class="support-link">contact our support team</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        &copy; 2025 ElevateU. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
